Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.15,0:01:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧？月影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.67,0:02:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勉強還好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  竟然還有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  烈火你快逃  這裡交給我就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.57,0:02:51.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.97,0:02:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我已經無希望得救
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.37,0:02:56.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能連累你也死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.64,0:03:01.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:05.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.58,0:03:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.12,0:03:10.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也死在這裡的話  誰來阻止它們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:16.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:39.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是紅蓮的年輕隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.42,0:03:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負有打倒妖魔的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.02,0:03:46.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.69,0:03:48.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  快逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們紅蓮是為了打倒妖魔而召集的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直屬於將軍大人的退魔機構
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.30,0:03:59.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連你也死在這裡的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有誰人來阻止他們呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.71,0:04:05.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.71,0:04:09.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.20,0:04:29.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你終於醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:31.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺如何呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:34.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.47,0:04:36.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你倒在河邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我費了好大的功夫才把你運來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.42,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有下毒的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:58.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:04:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  不客氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.38,0:05:18.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婆婆  婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.72,0:05:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人跑到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.27,0:05:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.75,0:05:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.09,0:06:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變態
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.72,0:06:36.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.47,0:06:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開她  妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.28,0:06:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.55,0:07:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟月影最先注意的就是這個村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近這裡頻頻發生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是妖魔所作的殺人事件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.43,0:07:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了收拾這些妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.43,0:07:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們預計跟分散的紅蓮眾會合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.97,0:07:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影應該有能力逃出那個困境
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與同伴一起等待我抵達
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:27.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我渺小的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.38,0:07:32.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？你還有臉到這裡來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只月影
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.25,0:07:38.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連救自己的女孩子都讓她被妖魔擄走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不敢相信了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.39,0:07:43.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  你說太重了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:48.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火想念月影的心是不下於我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我當然知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:52.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道  可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無言反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.87,0:07:58.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候被紅蓮帶走的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.01,0:08:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不曉得戰鬥的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只曉得學習戰鬥的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.61,0:08:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在每天持續的辛苦修行中
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:08.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經常關心我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.88,0:08:10.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支持我們的人是月影
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.29,0:08:15.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與小茜突然的語言衝突
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我的心更加沉痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.63,0:08:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼又出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.37,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在森林走著走著它就突然出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.37,0:08:30.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒命的逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是它  搶走我們村子姑娘的肯定是它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.44,0:08:37.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想沮喪到什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.85,0:08:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次救了你的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.79,0:08:46.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能被關在那個鬼地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.52,0:08:50.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  也許還來得及  我們趕快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個村裡的人說的  應該是這個附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個小屋很可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.60,0:09:02.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去查查看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.75,0:09:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面好像有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們一起衝進去速戰速決吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.02,0:09:18.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這太冒險了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:21.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果打不過的話怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.49,0:09:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時再說
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裡生活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.38,0:09:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前還有同伴的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.45,0:09:45.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是有天受到黑漆漆的傢伙攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑漆漆的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.25,0:09:51.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以現在就只剩下我一人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.99,0:09:53.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不努力的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:56.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會沒人保護森林啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.33,0:10:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要連不在的同伴的份也努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.20,0:10:06.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,估計我們的想法都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不害人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:11.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙畢竟還是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個鬼放在這地方  真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰曉得它何時會露出鬼的本性來襲擊人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.75,0:10:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不是長成這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.36,0:10:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村人看到我就怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.09,0:10:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會長角呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.57,0:10:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣一直笑著是不是就沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.78,0:10:55.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟那些會綁架村裡姑娘的鬼是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.59,0:10:58.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道那個鬼在哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.12,0:11:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這前方有片竹林
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:05.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個鬼就在竹林深處的洞窟裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.26,0:11:09.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要再來玩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我就招待你們吃森林裡的水果
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.40,0:11:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我們會再來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.68,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  為何不殺那個鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.28,0:11:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為他…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:35.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有做什麼壞事呀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且烈火你也…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:39.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對呀  就算是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不加害於人  就不是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想盡量避免無意義的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.57,0:11:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們還有必須打倒的惡鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.78,0:12:01.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.66,0:12:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太殘忍了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.83,0:12:47.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.24,0:13:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是從那洞窟傳來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.38,0:13:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡我們應付就足夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.11,0:13:06.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.35,0:13:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快要裂開了  我快壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.15,0:13:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:46.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:53.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我快壞掉了  快壞掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在倒在我腳下的這個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.32,0:15:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是在這慘狀之中的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的睡容就像普通女孩子一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我察覺到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是由於擁有特殊力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不惜偽裝自己的外貌  自己一個人隱居起來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.07,0:15:44.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這天真無邪的表情下面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:48.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知存在著多少黑暗的過去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.76,0:16:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫小遙啊  真辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.57,0:16:14.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無處可去的話  跟我們一起如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.17,0:16:20.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.92,0:16:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  這隻狗幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.45,0:16:34.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小茜  這是你撿的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:35.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想辦法管它呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.53,0:16:37.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好怕  好怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.26,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要湊近那麼臭的地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.33,0:16:44.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:49.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彩乃姐  這隻狗是雌還是雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看這只笨狗的行動  就知道不是雌的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.61,0:16:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼笨狗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.14,0:16:57.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  有取好名字了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他叫做千代丸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.15,0:17:00.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千代丸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.68,0:17:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼土氣的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦  我只是試著這麼喊喊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是  千代丸這名字太沒品味了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼你說什麼名字才有品味？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.63,0:17:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如叫小白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.77,0:17:20.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一點都不白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他紅豆怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.97,0:17:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.51,0:17:31.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是安大哥的安（同音）  是指紅豆麵包的紅豆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.85,0:17:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡吃紅豆麵包
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.59,0:17:43.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼大家一起喊名字
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用那隻狗有反應的名字怎樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.66,0:17:49.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來好像很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.80,0:17:51.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  那就試試看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一  二…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.27,0:18:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅豆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.68,0:18:08.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家在討論你的事  你還…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.62,0:18:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.49,0:18:15.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是叫千代丸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.06,0:18:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不著覺  可以進來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.60,0:19:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  剛才你為什麼不告訴大家？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.74,0:19:09.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟常人不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.95,0:19:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我自己也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.35,0:19:14.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼力量？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.22,0:19:17.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己為什麼變成那個樣子？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:22.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體內可能流著…醜陋的妖魔的血
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.16,0:19:26.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  我們確實是被組織起來打鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是今天我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.10,0:19:31.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見得所有的鬼都是壞人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:35.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙  你是為了被慘殺的村中少女們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:37.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺身對抗惡鬼的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.44,0:19:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用太在意大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且對我來說  你還是救命恩人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.18,0:19:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家找我一起走的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.92,0:19:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我就更難過  自己有事隱瞞大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是孤獨一人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.93,0:20:04.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙出現之前  我都還是過得很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們奪走了我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.07,0:20:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的朋友  父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及一切
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.81,0:20:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.88,0:20:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說有點不妥  應該說是我已記不起他們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.29,0:20:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你救了我之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是被另一位女性救了一命的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.23,0:20:34.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小時候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:36.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.03,0:20:38.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在森林中流浪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.24,0:20:43.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是紅蓮的首領收留我的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.97,0:20:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全身都是傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.44,0:20:49.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奄奄一息
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月影不眠不休照顧我  才救回我的小命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那之後  不論做什麼事我們都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:00.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.26,0:21:02.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起吃飯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:06.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把我當親弟弟一樣疼愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.73,0:21:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時又像疼愛自己的子女一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:15.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在紅蓮的辛苦修行  對我來說並不苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:18.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有她在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對失去記憶的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我唯一能傾心相訴的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.22,0:21:29.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到月影對你這麼重要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後換我來保護烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.35,0:21:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不讓鬼殺死你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.56,0:21:36.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.16,0:21:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我過言了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.50,0:21:45.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以  烈火你有月影…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這樣的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:51.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.71,0:21:52.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.71,0:21:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.25,0:22:02.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.39,0:22:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.79,0:22:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.07,0:22:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.74,0:22:28.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是骯髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.41,0:22:30.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我體內有鬼的血
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.01,0:22:32.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.95,0:22:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.55,0:22:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裡很髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.89,0:22:39.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難為情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.43,0:22:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  很髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.36,0:22:47.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.84,0:22:57.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.78,0:23:01.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行  別做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:08.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.18,0:23:12.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是…我是骯髒的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.39,0:23:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火  我這樣的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.19,0:23:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的  你就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.59,0:23:27.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.07,0:23:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.42,0:23:46.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.09,0:23:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.23,0:23:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:19.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.06,0:24:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好怪  自己好不對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.07,0:24:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.74,0:24:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.62,0:24:50.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烈火
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.42,0:24:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.62,0:24:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.12,0:24:54.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體中心好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.10,0:25:08.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好怪  我變得好怪
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.77,0:25:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.98,0:25:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.58,0:25:17.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.46,0:25:31.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.73,0:25:34.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  我真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.26,0:25:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好丟臉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.93,0:25:41.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  在哪邊呀  快點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.07,0:25:44.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外面在吵什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.81,0:25:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:51.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看就知道了  我們在打鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這算什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:56.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是以多欺小欺負沒抵抗的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.69,0:26:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.76,0:26:04.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拿這些來想請小哥你們吃
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.76,0:26:08.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我果然是不應該來人類居住的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.57,0:26:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  給你帶來麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.97,0:26:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趁現在
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.11,0:26:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們太沒用了  紅蓮
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.71,0:26:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還放鬼逃跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.78,0:26:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.18,0:26:29.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.39,0:26:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影舞
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.86,0:26:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人跟你一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.86,0:26:37.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,負有打鬼的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.26,0:26:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黑剛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.99,0:26:39.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.60,0:26:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也難怪你們不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.80,0:26:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們跟你們不同
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.73,0:26:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是老大的直屬部下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.47,0:26:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅蓮與我們負責間諜活動的人
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.07,0:26:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只擁有調查事件到解決事件之間的權限
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.68,0:26:58.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而黑剛則是完全的殺鬼部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.15,0:27:04.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的戰鬥力  恐怕還在紅蓮之上
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.56,0:27:08.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙我們帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:10.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想拿他怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.56,0:27:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我打到的獵物
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:15.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼處置與你無關
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.76,0:27:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.43,0:27:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
